Discover the exchange between Fatoumata Ly, Sista x Bold mentor,  co-founder of You're Welcome and VP of Singa France, and Céline Favy Huin, founder of Feel Object. 

Sista x Bold is a support programme created in May 2020 by @SISTA and Maison @VeuveClicquot to help women entrepreneurs recover from the effects of the global pandemic, preserve their businesses, and look to the future with confidence.

Thank you @fatouly and @celinefavyhuin for sharing your experience! For more inspiring stories, click on our link in bio.

#NEWMAKERSCOLLECTIVE #AROUNDTHEWORLD #LIVECLICQUOT #NEWMAKERSRECIPE
.
